<span class="taxonomyterm19091feed">NVRA instructions Virginia Spanish</span>


            
<p><strong>Instrucciones de los Estados — VIRGINIA</strong></p>


<p>
p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 4.5px 0.0px; line-height: 18.0px; font: 12.0px 'Arial Unicode MS'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000}
p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 4.5px 0.0px; line-height: 18.0px; font: 12.0px 'Arial Unicode MS'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 16.0px}
p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 4.5px 21.0px; line-height: 18.0px; font: 12.0px 'Arial Unicode MS'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000}
p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 21.0px; line-height: 18.0px; font: 12.0px 'Arial Unicode MS'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000}
p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 21.0px; font: 12.0px 'Arial Unicode MS'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000}
